      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and has plenty of adventures left in it! It shows a little bit of love from the years, but it\u2019s been well-cared for and runs like a dream. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
